'''维尼弗雷德·玛丽·比尔德'''[[女爵士|女爵士]]（{{lang-en|Dame Winifred Mary Beard}}，{{bd|1955年|1月1日|catIdx=Beard}}），英国[[古典學|古典学]]家，[[剑桥大学|剑桥大学]][[教授|教授]]，知名于对[[古罗马|古罗马]]的研究。2018年受封女爵士<ref name="LG">{{London Gazette |issue= 62310 |date= 9 June 2018 |page= B7 |supp= y }}</ref>。

==生平==
1955年1月1日生于[[什罗普郡|什罗普郡]][[溫洛克|溫洛克]]<ref Name="McCrum">{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/books/2008/aug/24/classics |title=Up Pompeii with the roguish don |first=Robert |last=McCrum |newspaper=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |date=2008-08-24 |accessdate=2015-07-29 |archive-date=2015-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150916202912/http://www.theguardian.com/books/2008/aug/24/classics |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她的母亲乔伊斯·艾米丽·比尔德是一所私立学校的校长<ref name=debrett/>。她的父亲罗伊·比尔德在[[什魯斯伯里|什魯斯伯里]]从事建筑工作<ref name=debrett>{{cite web |title=BEARD, Prof (Winifred) Mary |work=[[德倍礼|Debrett's]] |year=2008 |url=http://www.credoreference.com/entry/7696274 |accessdate=2008-07-16 |archive-date=2012-05-26 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67wJVoJAX?url=http://www.credoreference.com/loginwayf.do;jsessionid=1E28F6210671F054035DF40F152C4915.us-web-004 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

他在[[什鲁斯伯里|什鲁斯伯里]]高中（[[單性別教育|女子学校]]）上学<ref>{{cite news|last1=Laity|first1=Interview by Paul|title=A life in writing: Mary Beard, Britain's best-known classicist|url=https://www.theguardian.com/books/2007/nov/10/featuresreviews.guardianreview19|accessdate=2017-12-04|work=The Guardian|date=2007-11-10|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125034314/https://www.theguardian.com/books/2007/nov/10/featuresreviews.guardianreview19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她跟随{{tsl|en|Frank McEachran|弗兰克·麦克伊克兰}}学习诗歌<ref>{{cite web|last1=McCrum|first1=Robert|title=Interview with Mary Beard, the classical world's most provocative figure|url=https://www.theguardian.com/books/2008/aug/24/classics|website=The Observer|accessdate=2017-12-04|date=2008-08-23|archive-date=2015-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150916202912/http://www.theguardian.com/books/2008/aug/24/classics|dead-url=no}}</ref>。为了赚一些零花钱，她参加了考古夏令营活动<ref Name="McCrum"/>。

18岁入读[[剑桥大学纽纳姆学院|剑桥大学纽纳姆学院]]。她之前曾考虑过[[剑桥大学国王学院|剑桥大学国王学院]]，但得知大学该学院没有女性奖学金时便放弃了<ref name="McCrum"/>。她一直在学院深造，1982年获博士学位，论文《罗马共和国晚期的国教：基于[[西塞罗|西塞罗]]作品的研究》。

1979年至1983年，她在[[伦敦国王学院|伦敦国王学院]]担任助教。1984年回到剑桥，成为古典学院唯一的女讲师<ref name=debrett/>。次年出版与同事迈克尔·克劳福德的合著《共和国晚期的罗马》<ref>{{cite book |title=Rome in the Late Republic: Problems and Interpretations |last1=Beard| first1= Mary|last2=Crawford | first2=Michael | publisher = Gerald Duckworth | location=London | date=1985}}</ref>。她长期担任《泰晤士报文学增刊》的古典学编辑。她也活跃于[[互联网|互联网]]，与[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]合作拍摄了古罗马文明纪录片《[[相约古罗马|相约古罗马]]》等。

2004年，她成为剑桥大学古典学教授<ref name=CURep>{{cite journal |url=http://www.admin.cam.ac.uk/reporter/2004-05/weekly/5992/12.html |title=Appointments, reappointments, and grants of title |date=2005-03-02 |journal=Cambridge University Reporter |number=5992 |volume=CXXXV.20 |access-date=2020-10-07 |archive-date=2012-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120117201138/http://www.admin.cam.ac.uk/reporter/2004-05/weekly/5992/12.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2008年至2009年在美国[[加利福尼亞大學柏克萊分校|加利福尼亞大學柏克萊分校]]担任客座教授<ref>{{cite web |title=The Sather Professor |work=University of California, Berkeley Department of Classics |url=http://classics.berkeley.edu/people/sather.php |accessdate=2008-07-16  |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/69U4gOySq?url=http://classics.berkeley.edu/people/sather.php |archivedate=2012-07-28}}</ref>。2013年担任[[皇家艺术研究院|皇家艺术研究院]]古典文学教授<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/books/news/mary-beard-named-as-royal-academy-of-arts-professor-of-ancient-literature-8567757.html |title=Mary Beard named as Royal Academy of Arts professor of ancient literature |first=Nick |last=Clark |newspaper=The Independent |date=2013-04-10 |accessdate=2020-10-07 |archive-date=2017-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171204061359/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/books/news/mary-beard-named-as-royal-academy-of-arts-professor-of-ancient-literature-8567757.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

